      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      96.38,
      453.53,
      519.45,
      467.53
    ],
    "text": "This is now recognised by statute as well. In terms of sections 2 and 3",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      96.38,
      474.65,
      519.39,
      488.65
    ],
    "text": "of the Revocation of Irrevocable Deeds of Gift on the Ground of Gross",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      96.38,
      495.77,
      519.35,
      509.77
    ],
    "text": "Ingratitude Act, No. 5 of 2017, an irrevocable deed of gift may be",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      96.38,
      516.89,
      519.37,
      530.89
    ],
    "text": "revoked on the ground of gross ingratitude, only on an order made by a",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      96.38,
      538.01,
      519.46,
      552.01
    ],
    "text": "competent court, in an action filed by the donor against the donee",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      96.38,
      559.13,
      519.46,
      573.13
    ],
    "text": "within a period of ten years from the date of the execution of the deed",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      96.38,
      580.28,
      518.62,
      594.28
    ],
    "text": "and within two years from the date on which the cause of action arose.",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      96.38,
      613.4,
      519.46,
      627.4
    ],
    "text": "Slight ingratitude is not sufficient. There shall be gross ingratitude. No",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
